Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:40.60,DefaultTop,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Note: Kokeshi is a traditional Japanese wooden, decorative doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:32.75,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuo, turn off the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:36.13,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, the Monday Warm Fuzzy is just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:38.01,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Record it on the VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.01,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can watch it after the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.43,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.11,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,How's our brother doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.74,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,They said that he'll recover in a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.32,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:04.20,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.54,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:26.98,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,[Flower? of Kokeshi?]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:20.09,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,The 427th Katsumata-Family General Assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:23.43,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Today's topic is the 79th session of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:27.56,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we put flowers or a kokeshi at our entrance hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.73,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:34.48,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time assembling for such a silly reason so many times every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:38.82,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But, Katsuo, you usually read manga or sleep anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.99,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.16,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Katsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:46.95,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for a start, let's hear opinions from each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:50.58,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Who thinks we should put a kokeshi on the shoe shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.33,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.59,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.92,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.46,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:00.26,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,What about flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:01.55,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,That's 3-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.68,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,What did Kacchin say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.55,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,He said flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.81,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,3-3! Now we're even!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.68,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,The majority doesn't rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.19,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,We must come up with a solution that everyone will be satisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:13.85,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Dang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.61,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's decide it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.69,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuo, you're not serious enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.24,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.49,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Quit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.11,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.82,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:29.41,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, mother, I'll go, so would you remain seated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.50,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.50,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.87,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:35.88,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.25,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,You don't twist enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:38.92,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,The twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.09,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom : lost 62.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.80,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you win for once already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:50.14,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's hear the reasons why both teams push for their opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.64,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,First, the Flower Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.40,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Katsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.36,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.94,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But I went last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.53,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchin isn't here, so we don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.07,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:09.12,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Like, when someone comes to visit us, it's embarrassing to have a kokeshi at our entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.87,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,How is it embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.41,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a grandpa fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.75,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.33,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:23.01,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying that he doesn't want the mood to be destroyed when he brings home a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:23.67,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:27.30,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Katsuo! When did you find such a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.39,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're mistaking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.31,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what kind of relationship are you in with Urajima Katsuko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.94,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,whom you broght home on the 18th of last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.94,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,We were brainstorming on ideas for our school's open house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.90,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you lock your door?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.32,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you checking out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.78,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.58,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,We never come to a conclusion because we always go off a tangent like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.20,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mind on flowers and kokeshi for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:58.29,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,However, Katsuo, come to my study after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.42,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the Kokeshi Team!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.76,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:07.05,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,We must change water or switch flowers often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.34,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:13.22,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,My point is, either mom or I would end up doing those chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:16.44,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. It's a woman's job to take care of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:20.44,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, that's gender discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.94,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who's not willing to take care of them doesn't have any right to voice their opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.99,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, you don't have to take care of a kokeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.74,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to dust it once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:35.87,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,With the above points, I strongly, strongly push for a kokeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.67,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Kacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.46,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.50,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.09,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuo, say something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.38,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,She's so logical that I can't say anything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.93,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even say anything back to an elementary schooler?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.60,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, you dump everything on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.14,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Flower Team can't even respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.27,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.73,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's take an interval.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:02.15,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Both teams, scramble for strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.73,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is it going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.15,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.78,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Kokeshi Team has a big lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.62,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.37,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they'll outrun us at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:20.08,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,I would hate to have a kokeshi be the first thing I see when I step into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.13,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.55,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,After overtime, tired and beaten, opening the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.92,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine meeting your eyes with a kokeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.47,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Those cold eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.72,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,nihilistic mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.88,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,expressionless face...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.89,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,The exhaustion from the day would double!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.47,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A smiling kokeshi would be weird too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:41.40,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is there any good way to break their arguments?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.98,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What if we attack mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.40,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.03,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.57,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she doesn't have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.49,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If we convince her, we might be able to pull her to our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.03,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.99,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:07:01.87,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've heard from Katsumi and Katsuo, can I hear an opinion from mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.25,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.96,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.67,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you want a kokeshi in our entrance hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.89,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why a kokeshi over flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.43,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why a kokeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.10,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.43,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.19,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:31.95,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.06,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.23,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:13.11,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Come to think of it, this family started with that kokeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.91,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.07,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Katsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.07,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betraying my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.95,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:22.58,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,A kokeshi is like a cupid for mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.83,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be great to be greeted by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.79,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what you said erlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.46,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's two left in the Flower Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.01,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell! The adults are not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.80,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You change your minds so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.64,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll never give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.48,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have roses in our entrance hall, and show them to Urajima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.81,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:46.81,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.31,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.57,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.32,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.82,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.61,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame Katsuo for getting upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.53,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:01.74,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,about forgetting Katsue-san's kokeshi, and about changing your opinion so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.33,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.08,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll side with flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.13,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I have lots of free time anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:10.34,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of flowers will be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:11.96,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.34,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.34,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Katsukichi! Are you really a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.76,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Changing your opinions so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:22.31,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your ashamed as the head of the household, and as a husband?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.60,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.98,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I will never give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.69,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,We will have flowers in our entrance hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.65,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kokeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.32,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.82,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.57,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,The discussion will not end at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:41.70,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,You're to blame too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.17,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't talk about this, let's have luck decide the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:53.25,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a bet and the winning team will put up whatever they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.26,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a fair bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.76,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:00.64,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,The radio program that Kacchin works for starts soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.43,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Will the first letter that is read come from a man or a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.77,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's decide with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.60,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.60,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, which do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.27,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:09.77,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,A woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.77,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,All rihgt then. Turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.36,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.94,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:19.45,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,This is Maico, back from my weak of resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:23.37,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Let's spend our time together until our time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:28.58,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for a special treat, let me read a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.71,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,From pen name, Kacchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.09,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me, Maico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:39.88,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, my family has been having a small problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:45.06,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,It's about whether we should put flowers or a kokeshi in our entrance hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:50.85,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I am siding with flowers for now, but I'm not very particular about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:55.07,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,If my mother or sister wants to put a kokeshi, I don't have a strong reason to disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:59.61,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to hurt my father or my brother by siding with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:04.07,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand the fact that this friendly family is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.41,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Maico-chan, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.91,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,...there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.46,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.75,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you combine both sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:17.09,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, put a kokeshi holding flowers in your entrance hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:25.01,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,That way, everyone's wish will be kept, and I'm sure you can all see it with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.47,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,How's that, Kacchin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:31.31,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can see how much you care about your family, Kacchin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:36.11,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchin-san's family, stop fighting and have a peaceful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.82,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.36,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Jump ou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:45.12,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,That Kacchin... that's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.83,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.99,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.62,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,A kokeshi holding flowers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.54,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.00,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,But where would we find such a kokeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:00.96,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll start by asking at the dolly stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.01,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask at the seniors club too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:07.89,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,And if all else fails, let's ask some artists and have them make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.81,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:09.97,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.52,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,I have a hidden stash of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.23,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.40,Kacchin-mama,Katsue,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will have you help me out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.36,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.86,Default,Katsukichi,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.40,Default,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I need to stop the VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.37,Default,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see Kacchin tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.62,Default,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's chabashira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:29.95,DefaultTop,Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1} Chabashira - a stick of tea leaf, floating vertically inside the teacup - a sign of good luck/godd fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:07.49,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90\fad(500,500)\pos(460,215)\fs64}Maico's Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.94,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I found this really good "wanted" ad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.95,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I only have to work for 5 hours a day, and get paid 30,000 yen per day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.37,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The transportation fee and uniforms will be provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.16,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can even pick my uniform from nurse style or police style...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.71,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know what kind of job it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But the pay is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.38,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The next Android Ana Maico 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.55,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Je teame
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wish someone would say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:29.51,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I will only accept from a man 25 years or older, with an annual salary of 30,000,000 or above.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:24.59,Default,Maico's Diary,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Narrow\b0\frz13\3c&H6491A0&\c&H000000&\fs28\pos(450,320)}I read Kacchin-san's\N letter today.\N I tried, tried and tried\N to come up with my answer\N but I'm not sure if it\N helped Kacchin-san's family.\N Once he's out of the\N hospital, I'll ask him.
